Emmanuel Chuckwudi Afam Efuna Okoli (amụrụ n'October 13, 1998), nke a maara nke ọma site na aha mbụ ya bụ Yhaunai Takiyal, ma ugbu a bụ AugustWntr, bụ ónyé na-emepụta egwu dị iche iche, ónyé na-egwu egwu eletrọniki, na ónyé na-eti egwu si Baltimore, Maryland.
AugustWntr ewepụtala abọm studio abụọ Gold (2015) na Nature Theory (2016). O mepụtara ụdị dị iche iche, site na ọnyà ruo pop
O nyekwara aka remixes màkà ndị na-ese ihe dịka Drake na Flying Lotus.
N'afọ 2013, Okoli malitere ịgba egwu rap n'okpuru ónyé Azyn Porter
O wepụrụ nke a n'aka ndị na-akwado ya ruo ọtụtụ ọnwa, n'ikpeazụ kpughere njirimara ya ọnwa ole na ole mgbè a tọhapụrụ mixtape rap mbụ ya, Anti-Adventure.
A mụrụ AugustWntr Emmanuel Chuckwudi Afam Efuna Okoli na Ọktoba 13, 1998 na Baltimore, Maryland
Ọ gbanwere aha ya ọtụtụ ugboro na-eche na ọ bụ n'ihi ihe mgbu nke ntorobịa ya.
Mgbè ọ na-agafe site na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị gaa na ụlọ akwụkwọ dị elu, klas egwu kụziiri Okoli ime egwu ma n'oge na-adịghị ányá mee ka ọ banye na mmepụta egwu
Nnyocha ya n'ime ihe na-akụ malitere ịmepụta ụdị ọnyà na-etinye na boom bap hip-hop na ihe nkírí eserese.
Gold II bụ album squeal nke AugustWntr na ọla edo
Ka ọ dị ugbu a, abọm ahụ ga-agụnye ihe electronic, hip hop na trap instrumentals
A maghị ụbọchị ntọhapụ ugbu a, mànà a ga-eme ya n'afọ a
Nke a ga-abụkwa abọm mbụ nke AugustWntr nke a ga-ere na ụlọ ahịa egwu n'ịntanetị dịka: iTunes, Google Play, Spotify, wdg.
Mmetụta AugustWntr gụnyere Flying Lotus, Wondagurl, Eestbound, Kaytranada, na XXXTENTACION
Ọ bụ ezie na ụdị ya bụ ngwakọta hip-hop, ọnyà, electronic, na egwu nnwale.
